unique_sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was isolated with Trizol (Invitrogen Cat. No. 15596-026, Carlsbad, CA), according to the manufacturer's instructions. Total RNA was further purified using the Qiagen RNAeasy Mini Kit (Cat. No. 74104) according to the manufacturer's instructions
unique_sample_extract_protocol_ch2: Total RNA was isolated with Trizol (Invitrogen Cat. No. 15596-026, Carlsbad, CA), according to the manufacturer's instructions. Total RNA was further purified using the Qiagen RNAeasy Mini Kit (Cat. No. 74104) according to the manufacturer's instructions
unique_sample_label_protocol_ch1: One ug of total RNA was reverse transcripted to cDNA using T7 Promoter Primer and MMLV-RT. Then the cDNA was converted to aRNA using T7 RNA polymerase, which simultaneously amplifies target material and incorporates cyanine 3- or cyanine 5-labeled CTP (Two-Color Microarray-Based Gene Expression Analysis Protocol, Agilent).
unique_sample_source_name_ch2: prostate tissue (radical prostatectomy specimen),metastatic prostate cancer (obtained at rapid [warm] autopsy)
unique_sample_characteristics_ch2: tissue: benign prostate tissue (N),tissue: localized prostate cancer (T),tissue: metastatic castrate resistant prostate cancer (WA)
unique_sample_label_protocol_ch2: One ug of total RNA was reverse transcripted to cDNA using T7 Promoter Primer and MMLV-RT. Then the cDNA was converted to aRNA using T7 RNA polymerase, which simultaneously amplifies target material and incorporates cyanine 3- or cyanine 5-labeled CTP (Two-Color Microarray-Based Gene Expression Analysis Protocol, Agilent).
unique_sample_data_processing: Images were auto gridded, analyzed and data extracted using Agilent Feature Extraction Software (Version 9.1.3.1).  Spot values were normalized using the default linear-lowess normalization. LogRatio for all probes, which were used for subsequent analysis, were converted to log(2). Although the 1x44k and 4x44k arrays have the same probes, the 4x44k arrays have 10 replicates of some probes. unique_sample_hyb_protocol: 825ng of Cy3 and Cy5 labelled aRNA were hybridized competitively for 17 hrs in a 65 C hybridization oven (G2545A, Agilent) set to 10 rpm in a final concentration of 1X GEx Hybridization Buffer HI-RPM, according to the manufacturer's recommnded protocol (Two-Color Microarray-Based Gene Expression Analysis, Agilent).
